body:
i really don&#039;t have anything visually and gameplay wise, but imagine a champion who just really doesn&#039;t want to be on the rift?

Like they have a power that they can&#039;t control and the summoner is basically forcing them to fight.

His selection quite could be something like &quot;Please don&#039;t do this...&quot;

Or different attack quotes could be like:

&quot;Quick, run away!&quot;
&quot;Please dodge this..&quot;
&quot;I hope I miss.&quot;

Or something like that.

Just a small idea that came to mind that I had to share.
